---
title: Easy Indian Spiced Chicken & Roast Veggie Toss with Lemon Mayo & Flaked Almonds
description: Bring out the aromatic scents of a North Indian inspired spice mix and a warm palette of crispy roast veggies. Combine
them together to enrich your dinner with colour and flavour. You won’t be disappointed in how everything tastes so
undeniably good.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
